OL,4,G2200FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,5,     GAs Germany's resources dwindled,
OL,6,     GHitler and Goebbels promoted
OL,7,     GWonder Weapons as a path to
OL,8,     Gvictory. However, this blind
OL,9,     Gbelief in technology became a
OL,10,     Gmajor hindrance to the Nazi war
OL,11,     Geffort.
OL,12,G2300FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,13,     GHow did Hitler's narcotic use
OL,14,     Ginfluence his murderous regime
OL,15,     Gand delusional mindset? Did his
OL,16,     Gappetite for mind-altering
OL,17,     Gsubstances give the Allies
OL,18,     Gcrucial leverage in defeating the
OL,19,     GNazi regime?
